divs: Sighting DetailsWent outside to look at stars...I thought it was a planet..Then I saw it was moving fast like low flying airliner ,,no wings. No lights just a very brite light like it was blub...Look round at first then I could see some flat sides...It was 9:33 ,flew right over Reno airport.. from nw to se..
